Immerse yourself in the captivating world of streaming with my meticulously crafted Netflix-inspired landing page, meticulously constructed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The HTML structure defines a seamless layout featuring sections for featured content, categories, and compelling call-to-action buttons. Styled with responsive design principles, the CSS breathes life into the page with Netflix's signature color palette and layout aesthetics. JavaScript adds an interactive layer, allowing users to seamlessly transition to the sign-in page with the click of a button. The landing page serves as a visually immersive gateway, enticing users with placeholder images and text, while strategically placed links effortlessly guide them to the sign-in experience. This project not only showcases technical prowess but also promises users a seamless and engaging journey into the world of online streaming.





